Package org.acra.sender

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    ReportSender
    A simple interface for defining various crash report senders.
    ReportSenderFactory
    Factory for creating and configuring a ReportSender instance.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    EmailIntentSender
    Send reports through an email intent.
    EmailIntentSenderFactory
    Constructs an EmailIntentSender.
    HttpSender
    The ReportSender used by ACRA for http sending
    HttpSenderFactory
    Constructs a HttpSender with no report field mappings.
    JobSenderService
    Job service sending reports. has to run in the :acra process
    LegacySenderService
    Plain service sending reports. has to run in the :acra process.
    SendingConductor  
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    HttpSender.Method
    Available HTTP methods to send data.
  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    ReportSenderException
    This exception is thrown when an error occurred while sending crash data in a ReportSender implementation.
